    <div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even" property="content:encoded"><h4 class="textB latoH">FCA许可证和监管</h4>
<p class="pt-10">兴业投资（英国）由英国金融市场行为管理局（FCA）授权并监管，许可证号：186171。点击 <a target="_blank" href="https://register.fca.org.uk/ShPo_FirmDetailsPage?id=001b000000MfHH0AAN" class="textLink">此处</a> 查看我司许可证。下方为我司在FCA的登记信息： </p>

 <a class="license_type col-md-12  col-xs-12 mt-30" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#tab_lic1"><span class="latoR textW">联系详情</span><i class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-down textW pull-right"></i></a>

